gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: Abstract of the data product: This is an example dataset used to test AIXM parsing specifically for procedures (IAPs, SIDS, STARS). Not for operational use.

gmd:maintenanceAndUpdateFrequency.gmd:MD_MaintenanceFrequencyCode: Upon receipt of a valid change request amending the content of the dataset an update will be generated.

gmd:dataset.gco:CharacterString: Maintenance of the data: May be updated to support changes to test cases.

gmd:maintenanceNote.gco:CharacterString: No effort is made to depict real AIP data.

gmd:name.gco:CharacterString: The dataset is provided in AIXM version 5.1. (http://www.aixm.aero/schema/5.1)

gmd:useLimitation.gco:CharacterString: This is only intended to test AIXM parsing in specific scenarios.

gmd:useLimitation.gmd:MD_RestrictionCode: For software test purposes only. No guarantees are made of rigour or completeness. Do not use for aviation.

gmd:statement.gco:CharacterString: This dataset is handmade to test AIXM parsers. It is known to not be a complete example of every AIXM element or relation, and what is present may be flawed.
